---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="site-footer-inner">
    <p>
      Basado en principios de Benjamin Graham, Warren Buffett, Charlie Munger, Ray
      Dalio, Peter Lynch, Howard Marks y John C. Bogle. Contenido educativo, no
      constituye asesoría financiera individual.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">&copy; {year} Zeta &middot; Plan Financiero</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .site-footer-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }

  .muted {
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
